org.jetel.data.xml.mapping.runtime

Class XMLElementRuntimeMappingModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.data.xml.mapping.runtime.XMLRuntimeMappingModel
      • org.jetel.data.xml.mapping.runtime.XMLElementRuntimeMappingModel

  • public class XMLElementRuntimeMappingModel
extends XMLRuntimeMappingModel
    Class representing a mapping of XML element onto a data record. TODO: This class should be split into a hierarchy of classes, representing a mapping type (e.g. xml field -> clover field mapping vs. input field->output field mapping)
